  <brief_title>Spinal Deformity Intraoperative Monitoring.</brief_title>
  <official_title>SDIM: Spinal Deformity Intraoperative Monitoring. Understanding and Managing Intraoperative Neuromonitoring Changes During Spinal Deformity Surgery: a Prospective Interventional Study</official_title>
